OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid in Scotland: Mask    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frules will stay in force   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Funtil April                
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Scotland's rules on face coverings in  
OL,6, shops and on public transport will     
OL,7, remain in place until April due to a   
OL,8, rise in cases of Covid-19.             
OL,10,FAll other restrictions on businesses   
OL,11,Fand services are to move from legal    
OL,12,Frequirement to guidance from 21 March. 
OL,14,FBut First Minister Nicola Sturgeon said
OL,15,Fit would be "prudent" to keep mask     
OL,16,Frules in place due to a spike in cases.
OL,18,FThese will be reviewed again in two    
OL,19,Fweeks, and are likely to be converted  
OL,20,Fto guidance by 4 April.                
